{"id":"cmmel02o30001nrdj4we804rs","projectId":"cmmda4tdu00007oqcfk611gwg","campaignId":"cmmekujfn00012ihyp8y1mnei","type":"social_post","subtype":"feed_post","platform":"instagram","title":"How Zavis Powers Compassionate Ramadan Care","description":null,"status":"IN_REVIEW","currentVersion":1,"metadata":"{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"post_type\":\"product_feature\",\"target_audience\":\"Healthcare decision makers\",\"scheduled_time\":\"2026-03-12T18:00:00Z\",\"hashtags\":[\"ZavisHealth\",\"HealthTech\",\"PatientEngagement\",\"RamadanCare\",\"AIHealthcare\"],\"day\":6}","tags":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:37:03.363Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-06T07:46:31.160Z","versions":[{"id":"cmmel02o90003nrdjsq0j650v","assetId":"cmmel02o30001nrdj4we804rs","version":1,"filePath":null,"content":"Behind every great patient experience is the right technology.\n\nDuring Ramadan, Zavis helps healthcare providers:\n\nAutomated reminders timed for Ramadan schedules. No more 3 PM texts to fasting patients.\n\nSmart scheduling that prioritizes morning and post-Iftar slots automatically.\n\nHealth content personalized to each patient's conditions and fasting status.\n\nTelehealth options that reduce the burden on fasting patients.\n\nThe result: higher satisfaction, fewer no-shows, stronger patient relationships.\n\nThis is what patient-centered technology looks like.\n\n#ZavisHealth #HealthTech #PatientEngagement #RamadanCare #AIHealthcare #SmartScheduling #DigitalHealth #PatientSatisfaction #HealthcareInnovation #CompassionateTech","metadata":"{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"post_type\":\"product_feature\",\"target_audience\":\"Healthcare decision makers\",\"scheduled_time\":\"2026-03-12T18:00:00Z\",\"hashtags\":[\"ZavisHealth\",\"HealthTech\",\"PatientEngagement\",\"RamadanCare\",\"AIHealthcare\"],\"day\":6}","changelog":"Initial generation","createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:37:03.369Z","feedbacks":[]}],"brandChecks":[{"id":"cmmelc8s40001weagbsimr3md","assetId":"cmmel02o30001nrdj4we804rs","ve